	   <tr><td colspan=2>The only faction on Kerra is, not surprisingly, KerraIsland (or is it KerraRidge? I forget the EXACT name). I think I started out Indifferent as a Wood Elf Ranger, following Tunare. So, you have a LITTLE leeway before you hit Scowling.<br><br>Take heart, though. There's an easy, self-contained quest in Kerra itself you can do. Basically, you kill the Wharf Rat in the wharehouse down by the docks, then give the LORE NODROP Sharp Tooth to the Kerran out on the dock.<br><br>This yields the Rat Tooth Choker (3ac 2agi neck item, droppable but LORE) and a bit of Kerra faction.<br><br>There's another quest, Razorfish, that yields the Kerran Fishing Pole and some Kerra faction. But this one involves killing Razorfish (this fish is RARE - that's the problem) and giving the quest item to the Kerran out on the boat.<br><br>Arynduil Greyleaf<br>37th Ranger of Tunare<br>Norrathian Brotherhood, Erollsi Marr<br>&nbsp;<br>Arynduil<br>A Pathfinder on EMarr<br><br>"In a crowded Universe, when the talking turns to noise, you almost start laughing"</td></tr>
