	   <tr><td colspan=2>Warning- Spoiler (just trying to help the frustrated :)<br><br>(you really need a druid that can harmonize and group port)<br><br>Port to Tox.<br>Head West to the water.<br>Swim or fly to n457, p2470 and enter Kerra Island.<br>Head straight out and across the bridge then turn right and enter the camp on that side.<br>Enter door of hut at p546, p 159.<br>Go to far left corner and head down the stairs.<br>Go to second room, far left corner. (spawn and PH at p561, p194).<br>This room has a 15-20 minutes spawn time.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Hamed Grarr or PH Ahmed Shaman or his PH and 2-3 others in the room all spawn at once.<br>First rooms monsters never come in to attack so you can ignore them.<br><br>Hamed drops: <br>Hamed's Ring of Tears	current selling price: unknown<br>MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM <br>+15 MANA, +3 FR, +3 CR, +3 MR<br>WT: 0.1<br>Class: ALL<br>Race: ALL<br><br>and <br><br>Kerran Tribal Headband			current selling price: 35pp<br>AC: 1<br>+2 INT, +2 WIS, +10 MANA<br>WT: 0.1<br>Class: ALL<br>Race: ALL<br>and all others drops are garbage.<br><br>While helping a friend, I killed Hamed 3 times, first time got the ring and 2nd time garbage and third time got the headband.<br><br>-Sindee of Rocet Nife<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
